test_all_one_range:
assert [1] == [1, 1, 1, 1]
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1, 1, 1]
  + [1]
test_even_range:
assert [6, 8, 10, 12, 14] == []
  Left contains 5 more items, first extra item: 6
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [6, 8, 10, 12, 14]
test_odd_same_number:
assert [-11] == [-11, -11, -11, -11]
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: -11
  Full diff:
  - [-11, -11, -11, -11]
  + [-11]
